: contrast  ( b1 -- b1 )  green < abs white *  ;

  \ doc{
  \
  \ contrast  ( b1 -- b2 )
  \
  \ Convert color _b1_ to its contrast color _b2_.  _b2_ is
  \ white (7) if _b1_ is a dark color (black, blue, red or
  \ magenta); _b2_ is black (0) if _b1_ is a light colour
  \ (green, cyan, yellow or white).
  \
  \ See: `black`, `blue`, `red`, magenta`, `green`, `cyan`,
  \ `yellow`, `white`.
  \
  \ }doc

