' 8* alias papery  ( b1 -- b2 ) ?)

  \ doc{
  \
  \ papery   ( b1 -- b2 )
  \
  \ Convert paper color _b1_ to its equivalent attribute _b2_.
  \
  \ This word is an alias of `8*`, which is written in Z80.
  \ Its equivalent in Forth is the following:

  \ ----
  \ : papery  ( b1 -- b2 )  8 *  ;
  \ ----

  \ See: `brighty`, `flashy`, `attr>paper`.
  \
  \ }doc

